node.text:
❤️✨Tag someone you want to spend Valentine's Day with in this School Bus! Parked deep in the woods, with a big cozy fireplace, a tile & marble rainfall shower under a glass roof and even a full espresso bar! Imagine watching the sunrise and sunset from the roof-deck and falling asleep under the stars from the master bedroom! Where else could you ever wan't to be?❤️✨

Follow👉 @_justdoingmything_

node.text:
✨ Check out this incredible School Bus Conversion by @_JustDoingMyThing_ ✨

🚌💨
This 1999 Blue Bird School Bus is now a fully converted solar powered luxury tiny home that is full time traveling in the U.S.! Equipped with stainless steel appliances, a massive tile & marble shower, 56” electric fireplace, a full Espresso bar & more! 
 
Be sure to follow @_JustDoingMyThing_ for more! 
.
